y, &amp;#34;How much deterministic is Physics from Unity3d In 2019?&amp;#34;,Unity Forum,2020.Available:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//forum.unity.com/threads/how-much-deterministic-is-physics-from-unity3d-in-2019.711311/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="visible"&gt;forum.unity.com/threads&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;/how-much-deterministic-is-physics-from-unity3d-in-2019.711311/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt; [Accessed:2020-12-12]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[8]  Unity, &amp;#34;Burst User Guide&amp;#34;,Unity Manual, 2020.Available:&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docs.unity3d.com/Packages/com.unity.burst%401.0/manual/index.html%3F_ga%3D2.60059693.1096806956.1607653832-2097754989.1600740353" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="visible"&gt;docs.unity3d.com/Packag&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;es/com.unity.burst@1.0/manual/index.html?_ga=2.60059693.1096806956.1607653832-2097754989.1600740353&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;[Accessed:2020-12-12]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[9]   Glenn Fiedler, &amp;#34;Introduction to Networked Physics&amp;#34;, Personal Blog，2014. Available: &lt;u&gt;&lt;a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//gafferongames.com/post/introduction_to_networked_physics/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="visible"&gt;gafferongames.com/post/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;introduction_to_networked_physics/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;[Accessed:2020-12-12]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[10]  Glenn Fiedler，&amp;#34;Physics for Game Programmers : Network